_:N3a5294db4a5741019cb387347c3c2a78 <http://schema.org/description> "We are a statutory public corporation, sponsored by the Secretary of State for Defence, formed in 1986 by virtue of the Oil and Pipelines Act 1985. We manage, operate and maintain 6 Naval Oil Fuel Depots and a Petroleum Storage Depot on behalf of the Ministry of Defence. OPA is a public corporation of the Ministry of Defence ." .
